    "body": "A few ideas:\r\n1) You simply provide the \"old\" password, and ALL keys in the current (or specified --keystore-path) directory that are successfully decrypted are then updated to use the new password.\r\n\r\n2) You specify the exact validator and withdrawal key to be updated using filenames, and then prompt for old & new password.  A potential problem here is being able verify that the 2 keys are actually correlated to each other. ",
